patiently waiting for, namely, the destruction of antichrist; and now it
will be come, and patience will have its perfect work; see [Rev
13:10](../../../bib/kjv/rev013.htm#010.md)

here are they that keep the commandments of God; and not the inventions
of men, and the traditions of antichrist, but the ordinances of the
Gospel, as they were at first delivered, without any adulteration and
corruption; and who kept them because they were enjoined by God, and
from a principle of love to him, and with a view to his glory: these are
distinguished from the worshippers of the beast, and were preserved
throughout the apostasy; these are the witnesses who will now be risen,
and the remnant of the woman's seed, with whom the dragon made war by
