death, but by the resurrection of them from the dead; for when Christ
shall come in the clouds of heaven, and sit on the white cloud, or
throne, the dead in him will rise first, and the living saints will be
changed, and both will be caught up together, to meet the Lord in the
air; so that the earth will be reaped, and be clear of them, and there
