representation of a vintage.

[Revelation 14:17](../../../bib/kjv/rev014.htm#017.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_017">rev 14:17</span></span>

And another angel came out of the temple which is in heaven,.... It is a
strange conceit of Mr. Brightman's, that this angel is Thomas Lord
Cromwell, in the days of King Henry the Eighth, a sincere favourer of
